  "texts": [
    "These two parameters have been considered taking into account on the Münster classification of LoD [141].",
    "The final LoD score of the model was obtained by averaging these two features.",
    "On the one hand, geometrical fidelity refers to the detail on the surface of the 3D model.",
    "On the other hand, radiometrical fidelity refers to the detail in the reproduction of its visual properties.",
    "Lighting parameters were not considered as this is a factor outside the 3D model."
